text: Sair Khan (born 11 February 1988) is a British actress, born in Leeds, West Yorkshire, England. She is best known for playing the role of Alya Nazir in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street from 2014 onwards. In 2018, she appeared as a contestant on the ITV reality TV show I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!. ==Other websites== * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Actors from Leeds
